      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a3520;margin-bottom:10px;">Known for thick, syrupy coffee. Coorg Robusta is among India's best — earthy, bold, with a woody depth. The Arabica is chocolatey and full.</p>
      <div class="region-taste">Tastes like: Dark chocolate, earth, woody, full-bodied</div>
      <div class="region-tags">
