      <div class="region-stats">
        <div class="stat-row"><span>Body</span><span>Medium</span></div>
        <div class="stat-row"><span>Acidity</span><span>Bright</span></div>
        <div class="stat-row"><span>Sweetness</span><span>Very High</span></div>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a3520;margin-bottom:10px;">India's most celebrated specialty coffee. Grown by tribal farmers at high altitude, entirely organic. Won international awards in Paris. If you want to try something special, start here.</p>
      <div class="region-taste">Tastes like: Fruit, floral, light caramel, bright finish</div>
      <div class="region-tags">
