      <p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#4a3520;margin-bottom:10px;">One of India's most unique coffees. Green beans exposed to monsoon winds for weeks, creating an earthy, musty, incredibly full-bodied cup. A divisive taste — some love it deeply.</p>
