      <div class="roast-desc">Balanced · Chocolatey · Smooth</div>
      <p class="roast-notes">The sweet spot for most people. Roasted longer so sugars caramelise — giving you chocolate, caramel, and nutty notes. Not too bright, not too bitter. Works beautifully with or without milk.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px;">
        <span class="rtag">Chocolate</span><span class="rtag">Caramel</span><span class="rtag">Nuts</span><span class="rtag">Balanced</span>
