        <div class="brew-stat"><strong>5–7 min</strong>Brew Time</div>
      </div>
      <p class="brew-text">A stovetop aluminium pot. Water pressure forces through coffee grounds and collects in the top. Makes a thick, intense, espresso-style brew. Very popular in Indian homes. Affordable, durable, no electricity needed.</p>
