        <div class="brew-stat"><strong>₹800–3,000</strong>Device Cost</div>
        <div class="brew-stat"><strong>3–4 min</strong>Brew Time</div>
      </div>
      <p class="brew-text">Slowly pour hot water over grounds in a paper filter over your cup. Paper filters out oils — result is a clean, bright cup where you taste every nuance of the bean. This is how specialty café coffee tastes.</p>
      <div class="brew-perfect">✓ Perfect for: Araku or Nilgiris beans, curious home brewers</div>
