        <span class="brew-difficulty">Easy</span>
      </div>
      <div class="brew-stats">
        <div class="brew-stat"><strong>₹3,500–5,000</strong>Device Cost</div>
        <div class="brew-stat"><strong>2 min</strong>Brew Time</div>
